                                    text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;>&lt;b>AbbVie donates $233 for every home strikeout thrown by Cubs pitchers - honoring the 233 Americans diagnosed with cancer every hour.&lt;/b>&lt;sup>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-14-reg&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-16-reg&quot;>1&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
