                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>The campaign aligns with AbbVie's mission as a global biopharmaceutical company that discovers and delivers transformative medicines that help to solve serious health issues across several therapeutic areas including immunology, oncology, neuroscience and eye care, and products and services in our Allergan Aesthetics portfolio. In oncology, AbbVie's therapies for leukemias, lymphomas, lung and gynecological cancers are helping patients across the world.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
